data.description: Gorgeous country retreat with breathtaking views that includes a front yard view of Mt. Jefferson. Possible dual living: Main home has 3 bdrms, additional 4th bedroom/office & sprawling bonus room. Attached 1/1 cottage with separate entrance/ramp. You'll love the gourmet kitchen w/ abundant counter space & island, granite countertops & wide-plank hickory floors in kitchen, living & dining rooms. Expansive front & back porch areas & concrete patio for summer entertaining.
